{"title":"Shell编程：Shell变量的创建与使用","uid":"06a160e8900a1f6351a6a7991d1aeeb5","slug":"Linux-Shell01","date":"2020-04-02T03:44:40.000Z","updated":"2020-05-08T01:42:25.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Linux-Shell01.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"第一个shell脚本\"><a href=\"#第一个shell脚本\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"第一个shell脚本\"></a>第一个shell脚本</h2><ul>\n<li><p>新建文件hello.sh<br><code>vim hello.sh</code><br>输入下面代码</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">#!&#x2F;bin&#x2F;bash\necho &quot;Hello World !&quot;</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>保存退出，使用 <code>ls -l</code> 可以看到hello.sh没有执行权限，所以要先添加权限，然后在运行</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">chmod +x .&#x2F;hello.sh  #使脚本具有执行权限\n.&#x2F;hello.sh  #执行脚本</code></pre>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h2 id=\"shell变量\"><a href=\"#shell变量\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"shell变量\"></a>shell变量</h2></li>\n<li><p>定义变量时，变量名不加美元符号,如：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">your_name&#x3D;&quot;cjpnice&quot;</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>使用一个定义过的变量，只要在变量名前面加美元符号即可，如：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">echo $&#123;your_name&#125;</code></pre>\n<p>花括号可加可不加，最好加上，用来表示变量名的范围</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>定义只读变量,如：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">your_name&#x3D;&quot;cjpnice&quot;\nreadonly your_name</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>删除变量，如：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">unset your_name</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>Shell 字符串</p>\n<ul>\n<li>单引号<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><ul>\n<li>单引号里的任何字符都会原样输出，单引号字符串中的变量是无效的；</li>\n<li>单引号字串中不能出现单独一个的单引号（对单引号使用转义符后也不行），但可成对出现，作为字符串拼接使用。</li>\n</ul></blockquote>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">str&#x3D;&#39;this is a string&#39;</code></pre></li>\n<li>双引号<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><ul>\n<li>双引号里可以有变量</li>\n<li>双引号里可以出现转义字符</li>\n</ul></blockquote>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">str&#x3D;&quot;Hello, I know you are \\&quot;$your_name\\&quot;! \\n&quot;</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>拼接字符串</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">your_name&#x3D;&quot;cjpnice&quot;\n# 使用双引号拼接\ngreeting&#x3D;&quot;hello, &quot;$your_name&quot; !&quot;\ngreeting_1&#x3D;&quot;hello, $&#123;your_name&#125; !&quot;\necho $greeting  $greeting_1\n# 使用单引号拼接\ngreeting_2&#x3D;&#39;hello, &#39;$your_name&#39; !&#39;\ngreeting_3&#x3D;&#39;hello, $&#123;your_name&#125; !&#39;\necho $greeting_2  $greeting_3</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>获取字符串长度</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">string&#x3D;&quot;abcd&quot;\necho $&#123;#string&#125; #输出 4</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>提取子字符串</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">string&#x3D;&quot;cjpnice is a great people&quot;\necho $&#123;string:0:7&#125; # 输出 cjpnice</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>查找子字符串</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">string&#x3D;&quot;cjpnice is a great people&quot;\necho &#96;expr index &quot;$string&quot; n&#96;  # 输出 4</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>注意</strong>：以上脚本中 ` 是反引号，而不是单引号 ‘，不要看错了哦。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>Shell 数组</p>\n<ul>\n<li>定义数组,shell只有一维数组<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">array_name&#x3D;(value0 value1 value2 value3)</code></pre>\n或者<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">array_name&#x3D;(\nvalue0\nvalue1\nvalue2\nvalue3\n)</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>读取数组格式为：<code>$&#123;数组名[下标]&#125;</code><br>使用 @ 符号可以获取数组中的所有元素，例如：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">echo $&#123;array_name[@]&#125;</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>获取数组的长度</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"># 取得数组元素的个数\nlength&#x3D;$&#123;#array_name[@]&#125;\n# 或者\nlength&#x3D;$&#123;#array_name[*]&#125;\n# 取得数组单个元素的长度\nlengthn&#x3D;$&#123;#array_name[n]&#125;</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n","text":"第一个shell脚本 新建文件hello.shvim hello.sh输入下面代码 #!&#x2F;bin&#x2F;bash echo &quot;Hello World !&quot; 保存退出，使用 ls -l 可以看到hello.sh没有执行权限，所以要先添加权限，然后在...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.7k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Linux","slug":"Linux","count":4,"path":"api/categories/Linux.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Linux","slug":"Linux","count":4,"path":"api/tags/Linux.json"},{"name":"Shell","slug":"Shell","count":3,"path":"api/tags/Shell.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AAshell%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC\"><span class=\"toc-text\">第一个shell脚本</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#shell%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">shell变量</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"CHEN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109161140460.jpg","link":"/","description":"学无止境","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/cjpnice","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"Android开发：Fragment与Activity之间的通信","uid":"02546dabe3468067ae051607acdff58e","slug":"Android-Fragment1","date":"2020-04-03T02:55:12.000Z","updated":"2020-05-08T01:40:20.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Android-Fragment1.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"Activity向Fragment传值方法一：使用setArguments()和getArguments()方法传递Bundle 在Activity中使用fragment的setArguments（bundle）传到fragment。 public class MainActiv...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4.2k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Android","slug":"Android","count":16,"path":"api/categories/Android.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","count":25,"path":"api/tags/Java.json"},{"name":"Android","slug":"Android","count":16,"path":"api/tags/Android.json"}],"author":{"name":"CHEN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109161140460.jpg","link":"/",